{"prompt": "Design a modern site for a drone photography service. The aesthetic should incorporate a vibrant electric blue.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>AeroView Drone Photography</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #007bff; /* Vibrant electric blue */\n            --secondary-color: #e0f0ff; /* A lighter shade of blue */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --footer-background: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 20px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x600/007bff/ffffff?text=Stunning+Aerial+Views') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 100px 0;\n            position: relative;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            right: 0;\n            bottom: 0;\n            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .hero-content h2 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero-content p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid transparent;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n\n        .gallery {\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-background);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            border-top: 2px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>AeroView Drone Photography</h1>\n            <p>Capturing the World from Above</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n            <a href=\"#gallery\">Gallery</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h2>Elevate Your Perspective</h2>\n            <p>Professional drone imagery for real estate, events, and more.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get a Quote</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"services-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Real Estate Photography</h3>\n                    <p>Stunning aerial views to showcase properties in their best light.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Event Coverage</h3>\n                    <p>Unique perspectives for weddings, festivals, and corporate events.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Commercial & Industrial</h3>\n                    <p>Detailed aerial inspections and marketing content.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Cinematic Footage</h3>\n                    <p>Smooth, professional video to tell your story.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"gallery\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Gallery</h2>\n            <div class=\"gallery\">\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/007bff/ffffff?text=Property+View+1\" alt=\"Drone shot of a property\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/007bff/ffffff?text=Event+Aerial\" alt=\"Aerial view of an event\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/007bff/ffffff?text=Landscape+Shot\" alt=\"Drone shot of a landscape\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/007bff/ffffff?text=Cityscape+Night\" alt=\"Drone shot of a cityscape at night\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/007bff/ffffff?text=Industrial+Site\" alt=\"Aerial view of an industrial site\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/007bff/ffffff?text=Nature+Scene\" alt=\"Drone shot of a natural scene\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Ready to take your project to new heights? Contact us today!</p>\n            <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@aeroview.com\">info@aeroview.com</a></p>\n            <p>Phone: <a href=\"tel:+11234567890\">+1 (123) 456-7890</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 AeroView Drone Photography. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}